        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Which Method is Right for You?</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-900 mb-3">Choose Edibles If You...</h3>
